headline: Lincoln Day dinner celebrated
author: BELLEFONTAINE EXAMINER STAFF
sentences: He highlighted several court victories, where he and other attorney generals from across the country have challenged overreaching mandates from the Biden administration on vaccines, deportations and more.
Several candidates made their case to local conservatives during the Logan County Republican Lincoln Day Dinner Wednesday evening at the Winner Harvest Barn.
He also stressed the importance of supporting law enforcement agencies, instead of the Democratsâ€™ efforts to defund police.
